Pod Config

{

	{

		gLimit = 4.7

		}

			COLORDEFINITION
			{

				name = ASET_SWITCHER_MARK_POSITIVECOLOR

			}

				// Use warm-tone white to simulate incandescent lighting
				name = ASET_AIRCRAFTGAUGESCALE_ACTIVECOLOR

			COLORDEFINITION
			{

	}

@INTERNAL[VO1_IVA]
{
	// For some stupid reason, Unity won't load this IVA model using the MODEL node.
	MODEL
	{
		model = SquadExpansion/MakingHistory/Spaces/KVPods/KV1_IVA
	}
}
